{"tid":1539663,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:36:05.000Z","uid":125566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb9caf1ca17b8a17f165158ebd837207380430d","tid":1539663,"uid":125566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"如果6月9號就撒回既話 唔會發生之後既升級行動！<br />\n就唔會有手足比人捉！<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">被捕人士必須釋放！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n林病月餓 自己遲遲唔撒回 導致香港發生呢啲事情 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以林病應該問責下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n6月9號到宜家 明顯睇出警察如何濫權 監警會自己人查自己人根本就無用！ 而且黑警無編號 咁責任歸於誰？成立獨立調查還市民安心唔係更加重要咩？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">必須成立獨立調查/重組警隊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共所選既特首 根本無能力管理香港 並且香港人唔認同佢 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">基本法規定既雙普選必須馬上生效！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f9d1347621a395d3de0011ddd79b6d8c6f5ae54","tid":1539663,"uid":125566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8ac890d8d085d53dcdb41865860063c78fce665","tid":1539663,"uid":125566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊記五大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"76f9fe8bb3d67b4aa828b1a9cbb6dd5ab3eda261","tid":1539663,"uid":137157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"The FIVE demands of the protest<br />\n<br />\n1. Full withdrawal of the extradition bill <br />\n<br />\n2. A commission of inquiry into alleged police brutality <br />\n<br />\n3. Retracting the classification of protesters as &ldquo;rioters&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n4. Amnesty for arrested protesters <br />\n<br />\n5. Dual universal suffrage, meaning for both the Legislative Council and<br />\n    the Chief Executive <br />\n<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS,<br />\nNOT ONE LESS.<br />\nLIBERATE HONG KONG,<br />\nREVOLUTION OF OUR TIMES."},{"pid":"e5f372589a6a5ef7c199dcb55c04a2628ac622fe","tid":1539663,"uid":227320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:27:12.000Z","msg":"被捕人士必須釋放！！"},{"pid":"14b16865e11ae8e7a9993c173655fca65a8d7c5b","tid":1539663,"uid":287602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺<br />\n一<br />\n不<br />\n可"},{"pid":"51017c0fa4ae70abfff0c0fcea6ec208f3e7aa12","tid":1539663,"uid":125566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"缺一不可！"}]}